body:
Then how do you ping something like...

&quot;Lets take dragon and then mid tower&quot;
&quot;After we take Baron we should all back and then rush top&quot;
&quot;I&#039;m going to farm a little more, don&#039;t engage&quot;
&quot;Yasuo, you go top. The rest of us are going to stay here in bot&quot;
&quot;Blitzcrank, next teamfight be sure to grab Vayne&quot;
&quot;I&#039;m going to roam, play safe&quot;
&quot;Hey mid, want blue?&quot;
&quot;Lets focus Nasus next teamfight&quot;
&quot;Should we go for mid inhibitor or should we go straight for the inner towers?&quot;
&quot;Top, do you want to laneswap?&quot;
&quot;Ashe can you build a Runaan&#039;s Hurricane next?&quot;
&quot;They have a ton of AP, so lets all build MR&quot;

Yes, I know these are extremely specific, but that is the point. Anything more complicated than &quot;let&#039;s kill this thing&quot; can&#039;t be completed by just pings.
